A '''platebody''' is a type of [[armour]] worn mainly by [[Combat classes#Warrior|warriors]]. Among [[melee]] [[attack types]], platebody provides good defence against the slash attack type but is more vulnerable to the crush attack type.

Platebodies give players penalties towards [[ranged]] attacks and penalties towards [[magic]] defence. However, platebodies have very good defence against ranged as well as melee attacks.

Platebodies are made with the [[Smithing]] skill or purchased at [[platebody shops]], which is identified by the [[File:Platebody shop icon.png]] icon on the map. This piece of armour will interfere with [[Ava's accumulator]] and [[Ava's attractor]].

